metadata.name: Officially Intelligent NFT #1
metadata.description:
💡OFFICIALLY INTELLIGENT NFT is a collection of 1500 unique, mysterious Light Bulbs on the Ethereum network

💡FREE public Alpha and holders-exclusive Alpha
💡All Whitelist giveaways from other projects for collabs after mint will be voted on before the spots given to the community.. To prevent Rug Pull WL giveaways.
💡Solve riddles and equations for ETH rewards (before and after Mint)
💡Proper trading tool and Alert Bots to keep us ahead of the market. (Fomo , Minting , Sniping , ETC.)
💡Minter for the 1/1 Einstein trait will receive .5 ETH
💡Voters Rights. Voters right will be all future utility to all holders who delist or list above 5 ETH will have full decision making in the next utilities with the project.

💡This project is about learning from each other and building with each other. Always Remember Genius… Coming together is the beginning. Keeping together is the progress. Working together is Success.✨🤝
